text: @gluroo how many carbs in a samosa?

{"text":"A typical samosa contains approximately 15-25 grams of carbs, depending on size and ingredients. Let's assume 20 grams for calculation purposes unless you know the specific carb content. How many samosas are you having?"}

{"text":"Gluroo is a collaborative diabetes management app designed to help manage blood glucose levels and diabetes care more effectively. It offers integration with various Continuous Glucose Monitors (CGMs) and insulin pumps, such as Omnipod and Dexcom, and supports various platforms including iOS and Android. Gluroo makes it easy to share glucose data with family, caregivers, and healthcare providers in real-time.\n\nYou can log meals, insulin doses, exercise, and more, and set reminders for various tasks. The app also supports calendar integration, alerts for blood glucose levels, and provides tools for tracking and analyzing diabetes data. For more detailed information, you can visit their support and blog articles [here](https://gluroo.com/support/) and [here](https://gluroo.com/blog/glucrew/introducing-gluroo/)."}
